    "created_at": "2015-05-31T13:50:23Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-05-31T13:56:31Z",
    "body": "I would estimate that we would be dealing with file sizes at 50mb and up from what I have seen so far.\n\nI like the idea of using SQLite for the SQL aspects but I haven't quite figured out how I would save that into AppData. We are already using the FS module and app data for a config file, probably move this into local storage.\n\nIt looks like FS would be able to save down the SQLite DB. Hopefully I'll be able to play with that concept and see where it gets me.\n"
